content: I'm looking for some advice on choosing a coffee table. I've been browsing online, but there are so many options. I'm particularly interested in something with a wooden finish and clean lines, kind of like the mid-century modern aesthetic. Oh, and by the way, I just cleared out my home office to make room for a new standing desk, and I realized I'd been holding onto my old college dorm room desk for way too long - it was taking up too much space for about 5 months before I finally moved it out.
